results.name: Product of digits of (n written in base 4).
link: Seiichi Manyama, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
formula: G.f. A(x) satisfies: A(x) = x * (1 + 2*x + 3*x^2) * (1 + A(x^4)).
